description: This agent allows your app to help users search for flights, book flights and answer FAQ.

User: Actually, returning July 25.

User: Find me the cheapest flights to London for October 3.
User: Are there still some non-stop flights to Colorado for Christmas?
User: Search for refundable flights only.
User: When will the flight from Rome depart?
User: Check status of a flight.

User: Can I get a map of LAX?
User: Can I take an umbrella on the flight?
User: What's the maximum baggage size?
User: I need special assistance.
